rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0001
rows.name:
You have the air of a shop owner
about you.

rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0002
rows.name:
What do you think happens if you
buy a shop's entire stock?

rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0003
rows.name:
The shopkeeper will be so impressed
by your love for their business, they'll
ask you to become the shop's owner.

rows.label: tlk41400011_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Becoming a shop owner costs quite
a bit of money, but you get a lot of
benefits out of it!
